To delete a MongoDB Search index on a collection using the [Java
Driver](java/sync/current/indexes),
use the `dropSearchIndex()` method:

The following sample application deletes the specified MongoDB Search index
on the specified collection.

```java
import com.mongodb.client.MongoClient;
import com.mongodb.client.MongoClients;
import com.mongodb.client.MongoCollection;
